              https://doi.org/10.1007/BF00624348</a></div><div class="citation-links"><div class="google-scholar-ref-link js-ref-link"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=E-vector%20sensitivity%20patterns%20in%20the%20goldfish%20optic%20tectum&amp;author=T.%20H.%20Waterman&amp;author=K.%20Aoki&amp;publication_year=1974&amp;journal=J.%20comp.%20Physiol.&amp;volume=95&amp;pages=13-27" target="_blank">Google Scholar</a></div><div class="crossref-doi js-ref-link"><a class="openInAnotherWindow" href="http://dx.doi.org/10.1007/BF00624348" target="_blank">Crossref</a></div><div class="adsDoiReference hide"><a class="openInAnotherWindow" href="http://adsabs.harvard.edu/cgi-bin/basic_connect?qsearch=10.1007%2FBF00624348" target="_blank">Search ADS</a></div><div class="xslopenurl empty-target"><span class="inst-open-url-holders" data-targetId="10.1007%2FBF00624348"> </span></div> </div></div></div></div></div><div content-id="jexbio_198_2_325c39" xmlns:helper="urn:XsltStringHelper"><div class="ref false"><div data-modal-id="jexbio_198_2_325c39" class="ref-content "><div class="citation mixed-citation"><span class="person-group"><span class="name string-name"><div class="surname">Waterman</div>, <div class="given-names">T. H.</div></span> and <span class="name string-name"><div class="surname">Hashimoto</div>, <div class="given-names">H.</div></span></span> (<div class="year">1974</div>.). <div class="article-title"><em>E</em>-vector discrimination by the goldfish optic tectum</div>. <div class="source"><em>J. comp. Physiol.</em></div> <div class="volume">95</div>, <div class="fpage">1</div>–<div class="lpage">12</div>. <div class="pub-id-doi"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1007/BF00624347" class="link link-pub-id-doi openInAnotherWindow" target="_blank">
